    "No a priori hypotheses were preregistered for study 3, which is descriptive and exploratory.",
    "Power AnalysesFor studies 1 and 2, assuming comparisons between two groups of n=100 each and α of.05, a priori sensitivity analyses for 2-tailed independent sample t tests performed in G*Power indicated a power of 0.8 to detect small to medium effect sizes (Cohen d=0.398).",
    "A priori power analyses were not performed for study 3, given its exploratory nature.",
    "Ethical ConsiderationsThis study did not involve human subjects research; therefore, no ethical approval was required.",
